title: Prep spotlight: Matter, O'Donnell, Gannon, Hayden
text:
AGE: 17 
SPORT: Volleyball 
THE HIGHLIGHTS: Hayden, who has committed to the University of Nevada-Las Vegas, has made 312 kills this season, bringing her career total to 1,485. She also has 13 blocks, 37 service aces and 157 digs this year for the Tigers, who are 14-2. She had 31 kills in a victory over Waconia on Monday. 
For her career, Hayden has made 180 ace serves, 88 blocks and 872 digs for the top-ranked team in Class AA. 
The Prep Spotlight is a feature that runs every Sunday to highlight high school student-athletes who have performed well the previous week. If you know someone who deserves to be in this feature, please send an email to sports@mankatofreepresscom with the information. Make to include the words Prep Spotlight in the subject box.
